quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,33,aur jab logon ko takleef pahunchti hai to apne perwar-digaar ko pkarte aur isi ki taraf rujoo hotay hain. phir jab woh un ko apni rehmat ka maza chkhata hai to aik firqa unn mein se apne perwar-digaar se shirk karne lagta hai
  30,34,taakay jo hum ne un ko bakhsha hai uss ki nashukri karen so ( kher ) faiday اutha loo anqareeb tum ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom ho jaye ga
  30,35,kiya hum ne un par koi aisi Daleel nazil ki hai ke unn ko khuda ke sath shirk karna batati hai
  30,36,aur jab hum logon ko apni rehmat ka maza chukhate hain to uss se khush ho jatay hain aur agar unn ke amlon ke sabab jo unn ke hathon ne agay beje hain koi gznd puhanche to na umeed ho kar reh jatay hain
  30,37,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda hi jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq farakh karta hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang karta hai. bay shak is mein imaan laane walon ke liye nishanain hain
  30,38,to ehley qaraabat aur mohtajon aur musafiron ko un ka haq dete raho. jo log razaye khuda ke taalib hain yeh unn ke haq mein behtar hai. aur yahi log nijaat haasil karne walay hain
  30,39,aur jo tum sood dete ho ke logon ke maal mein afzaish ho to khuda ke nazdeek is mein afzaish nahi hoti aur jo tum zakaat dete ho aur uss se khuda ki Raza mandi talab karte ho to ( woh mojab barket hai aur ) aisay hi log ( apne maal ko ) do chand sah chand karne walay hain
  30,40,khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko pedakiya phir tum ko rizaq diya phir tumhe maaray ga. phir zindah kere ga. bhala tumahray ( banaye hue ) sharikon mein bhi koi aisa hai jo un kamon mein se kuch kar sakay. woh pak hai aur ( is ki shaan ) un ke sharikon se buland hai
  30,41,khushki aur tri mein logon ke aamaal ke sabab fasaad phail gaya hai taakay khuda unn ko unn ke baaz aamaal ka maza chakha-ay ajab nahi ke woh baz ajayeen
